29:45.551 --> 29:47.774
nice of you to do that. We've made good friends over 
here. So Exxon now really is defining its mission.

29:55.135 --> 29:58.058
I was on the committee that split chemicals from 
the oil side. We divided up all the assets and

29:58.138 --> 30:01.382
things like that. And this was in 59? 1961. 61. And

30:04.425 --> 30:14.236
I had been on the committee to divide up assets. 
